AllMatchersParameterValueGetter, AnyMatcherParameterValueGetter, CriteriaCollectionValueGetter, NotMatcherParameterValueGetter, OnlyOneMatcherParameterValueGetter, ParameterValueGetter.DefaultParameterValueGetter, ParameterValueGetter.DurationParameterValueGetter, ParameterValueGetter.TranslatedDescriptionParameterValueGetter, PresenceParameterValueGetter, ThrowableValueGetter, TypesValueGetter
public interface ParameterValueGetter<T>
Converts some value to a readable parameter of a step or to fragment of step description. It is supposed to be used by the reading of StepParameter.makeReadableBy() and DescriptionFragment.makeReadableBy()
